data.description: Amazing 3 bedroom/ 2 bath home in the much sought after Eagle's Landing neighborhood of The Vineyards. Wide open family area & hardwood floors is just the beginning of the warm charm that you will find. The large kitchen with hard surface counter tops and lots of cabinet space, leads right into the formal dining room. The secondary bedrooms offer lots of space and the master features a spacious bath with dual vanities and garden tub. Want peace and quiet? The private fenced back yard features just that as you entertain on the back patio.
